《'''忐忑'''》（{{lang-en|''As Above, So Below''}}）是一部2014年美國[[恐怖片|恐怖片]]，為[[約翰·艾瑞克·道鐸|約翰·艾瑞克·道鐸]]執導並與弟弟德魯合作編劇。電影主要以[[拾得錄像_(片種)|拾得錄像]]的方式拍攝。由{{link-en|波迪塔·韋克絲|Perdita Weeks}}、{{link-en|班·費德曼|Ben Feldman (actor)}}、[[艾德恩·霍吉|艾德恩·霍吉]]、{{link-en|法蘭索瓦·西維爾|François Civil}}、Marion Lambert和Ali Marhyar主演<ref>{{Cite news |first=Justin |last=Kroll |url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/legendary-universal-date-guillermo-del-toros-crimson-peak-for-oct-2015-1201078647/ |title=Legendary, Universal Date Guillermo del Toro's 'Crimson Peak' for October 2015 |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |date=2013-01-30 |accessdate=2014-03-07 |archive-date=2017-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170729015129/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/legendary-universal-date-guillermo-del-toros-crimson-peak-for-oct-2015-1201078647/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|script-title=en:Universal Pulls ‘The Loft’ From Sked, Moves Legendary Pic ‘As Above/So Below’ Into Slot|author=The Deadline Team|date=2014-06-26|url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/06/universal-pulls-the-loft-from-sked-moves-legendary-pic-as-aboveso-below-into-slot/|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|accessdate=2016-07-18|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714225938/http://www.deadline.com/2014/06/universal-pulls-the-loft-from-sked-moves-legendary-pic-as-aboveso-below-into-slot/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《忐忑》於2014年8月29日在美國上映。電影為[[傳奇影業|傳奇影業]]製作，[[環球影業|環球影業]]負責發行，而這也是傳奇與環球合作的首部電影<ref>{{Cite news |first=Justin |last=Kroll |url=http://variety.com/2013/film/news/legendary-and-the-dowdle-brothers-to-make-archaelogical-found-footage-pic-exclusive-do-not-post-1200375118/ |title=Legendary and the Dowdle Brothers to Make Low Budget Thriller |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |date=2013-04-22 |accessdate=2014-03-07 |archive-date=2019-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191130184258/https://variety.com/2013/film/news/legendary-and-the-dowdle-brothers-to-make-archaelogical-found-footage-pic-exclusive-do-not-post-1200375118/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==劇情==
兩位考古學家與數名年輕人前往巴黎地下墓穴中尋找失落的寶藏，竟引發一連串駭人事件...<ref>{{@movies|id=faen22870612|title=忐忑 As above so below}}<!-- 2016-07-18 accessdate --></ref>。

